library(gapminder)
a2007 <- gapminder[gapminder$year=="2007",] 
asia <- a2007[a2007$continent == "Asia",]
africa <- a2007[a2007$continent == "Africa",]
americas <- a2007[a2007$continent == "Americas",]
europe <- a2007[a2007$continent == "Europe",]
oceania <- a2007[a2007$continent == "Oceania",]

nradius <- sqrt(asia$pop/pi)
n2radius <- sqrt(africa$pop/pi)
n3radius <- sqrt(americas$pop/pi)
n4radius <- sqrt(europe$pop/pi)
n5radius <- sqrt(oceania$pop/pi)

par(mfrow = c(3,2))

symbols(asia$gdpPercap, asia$lifeExp, circles = nradius, las=1, inches = .325,fg = "white", bg = rainbow(10), cex.axis = 0.8, xlab = "亞洲人均GDP", ylab = "亞洲預期壽命", main = "2007年亞洲預期壽命與人均GDP的氣泡圖", ylim = c(40,90))
text(asia$gdpPercap, asia$lifeExp, asia$country,cex = 0.5)

symbols(africa$gdpPercap, africa$lifeExp, circles = n2radius, las=1, inches = .325,fg = "white", bg = rainbow(10), cex.axis = 0.8, xlab = "非洲人均GDP", ylab = "非洲預期壽命", main = "2007年非洲預期壽命與人均GDP的氣泡圖", ylim = c(40,90))
text(africa$gdpPercap, africa$lifeExp, africa$country,cex = 0.5) 

symbols(americas$gdpPercap, americas$lifeExp, circles = n3radius, las=1, inches = .325,fg = "white", bg = rainbow(10), cex.axis = 0.8, xlab = "美洲人均GDP", ylab = "美洲預期壽命", main = "2007年美洲預期壽命與人均GDP的氣泡圖", ylim = c(40,90))
text(americas$gdpPercap,americas$lifeExp, americas$country,cex = 0.5)

symbols(europe$gdpPercap, europe$lifeExp, circles = n4radius, las=1, inches = .325,fg = "white", bg = rainbow(10), cex.axis = 0.8, xlab = "歐洲人均GDP", ylab = "歐洲預期壽命", main = "2007年歐洲預期壽命與人均GDP的氣泡圖", ylim = c(40,90))
text(europe$gdpPercap, europe$lifeExp, europe$country,cex = 0.5)

symbols(oceania$gdpPercap, oceania$lifeExp, circles = n5radius, las=1, inches = .325,fg = "white", bg = rainbow(10), cex.axis = 0.8, xlab = "大洋洲人均GDP", ylab = "大洋洲預期壽命", main = "2007年大洋洲預期壽命與人均GDP的氣泡圖", ylim = c(40,90))
text(oceania$gdpPercap, oceania$lifeExp, oceania$country,cex = 0.5)

library(lattice)
summary(gapminder$lifeExp)
gapminder.new <- gapminder[gapminder$gdpPercap < 50000,]
xyplot(lifeExp~gdpPercap|year, data = gapminder.new, layout=c(4,3),
       ##panel=function(x,y){  
  ##panel.xyplot(x, y)                    
  ##panel.abline(h = median(y), lty = 2)  
})
gapminder.new$year <- as.character(gapminder.new$year)
q <- xyplot(lifeExp~gdpPercap|year, data = gapminder.new, layout=c(4,3),
            panel=function(x,y){  
              panel.xyplot(x, y)                    
              panel.abline(h = median(y), lty = 2)  
            })
update(q, index.cond = list(c(9:12, 5:8, 1:4)), main = "1952~2007預期壽命與人均GDP的散布圖")

bwplot(lifeExp~continent|year, data = gapminder.new , layout=c(4,3),col ="gray")
w <- bwplot(lifeExp~continent|year, data = gapminder.new , layout=c(4,3),col ="gray")
update(w, index.cond = list(c(9:12, 5:8, 1:4)), main = "1952~2007五大州的預期壽命盒形圖", box.ratio = 1.5, col ="gray", xlab = "洲名")
